Client Metric Thresholds Crossed

The following clients have crossed metric thresholds on #{@calculation_date.strftime('%B %d, %Y')}:

- @crossings.each do |metric_name, snapshot_info|
  \
  #{metric_name}
  = '-' * metric_name.length
  #{snapshot_info[:total_count]} #{'client'.pluralize(snapshot_info[:total_count])} crossed the threshold for this metric.
  - if snapshot_info[:truncated]
    (Showing first 50)

  - snapshot_info[:data].each do |data|
    \
    Client ##{data[:entity_id]}: #{client_url(id: data[:entity_id])}
    - if data[:previous_value]
      Previous Value: #{data[:previous_value]}
      New Value: #{data[:current_value]}
      - change = data[:current_value] - data[:previous_value]
      - sign = change > 0 ? '+' : ''
      Change: #{sign}#{change}
    - else
      New Value: #{data[:current_value]}
      (New baseline)

